{"word":"Solomon","slug":"solomon","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Solomon</b> - king of Israel, son of David and Bath-sheba<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=5&verse=14'>2Sa 5:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=12&verse=24'>2Sa 12:24</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=1&verse=11'>1Ki 1:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=1&verse=30'>1Ki 1:30</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=1&verse=39'>1Ki 1:39</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=2&verse=1'>1Ki 2:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=3&verse=1'>1Ki 3:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=4&verse=1'>1Ki 4:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=5&verse=1'>1Ki 5:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=6&verse=1'>1Ki 6:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=7&verse=1'>1Ki 7:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=8&verse=1'>1Ki 8:1</a><p/>     <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=28&verse=20'>1Ch 28:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=29&verse=23'>1Ch 29:23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=1&verse=1'>2Ch 1:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=2&verse=1'>2Ch 2:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=3&verse=1'>2Ch 3:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=5&verse=1'>2Ch 5:1</a><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=6&verse=1'>2Ch 6:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=7&verse=1'>2Ch 7:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=8&verse=1'>2Ch 8:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=9&verse=1'>2Ch 9:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=9&verse=23'>2Ch 9:23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=9&verse=31'>2Ch 9:31</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=12&verse=42'>Mat 12:42</a><p/>-- \"The Man of Wisdom and Folly\"<p/>His Wisdom see<p/>-- in his wise choice<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=3&verse=5'>1Ki 3:5-9</a><p/>-- In judicial insight<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=3&verse=16'>1Ki 3:16-28</a><p/>-- In surpassing other wise men<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=4&verse=29'>1Ki 4:29-31</a><p/>-- In uttering proverbs and discourses<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=4&verse=32'>1Ki 4:32-34</a><p/>-- In erection of the temple<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=5&verse=1'>1Ki 5:1-18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=6&verse=1'>1Ki 6:1-38</a><p/>-- In his prayer of dedication<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=8&verse=22'>1Ki 8:22-53</a><p/>His Folly shown<p/>-- In luxurious living<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=4&verse=22'>1Ki 4:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=4&verse=23'>1Ki 4:23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=10&verse=21'>1Ki 10:21</a><p/>-- In marrying heathen women<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=11&verse=1'>1Ki 11:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=11&verse=2'>1Ki 11:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=13&verse=23'>Neh 13:23-26</a><p/>-- In excessive sensuality<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=11&verse=3'>1Ki 11:3</a><p/>-- In oppressing the people<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=12&verse=4'>1Ki 12:4</a><p/>-- In sanctioning idolatry<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=11&verse=4'>1Ki 11:4-7</a>"}]}